folder: East River Drive & 81st Street (East), Manhattan, NY
text:
East River Drive, north from East 81st Street, showing a portion of the new circumfrential highway and the surrounding locale at this point. The apartment houses
above constitute Gracie Square.
September 29, 1940
No's. 1-2-3
P. L. Sperr

folder: East River Drive & 81st Street (East), Manhattan, NY
text:
East River Drive, at the foot of East 81st Street, showing details of the over-pass above the new viaduct.
In the background are the Triboro and Hellgate Bridges.
September 29, 1940
No's. 1-2
P. L. Sperr
